{"tid":430052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林海峰：受傷仍堅持","createTime":"2017-10-09T13:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T13:02:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f62968613507a9a8ff9788cb0473140d4db22d","tid":430052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20171009/20176540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20171009%2F20176540&d=FlAT4ac8BheUc0HY1aS77jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c458178e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20171009%2F20176540&h=a9221b62\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20171009/20176540</a><br />\n<br />\n林海峰：受傷仍堅持<br />\n<br />\n9,367<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/09ec1p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F09ec1p7.jpg&h=87500c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林海峰指曹星如打少一隻眼仍然堅持，好值得支持。<br />\n<br />\n曹星如前晚決戰河野公平，吸引林海峰、杜汶澤、徐濠縈、鄭希怡、何超蕸、劉浩龍、馮允謙、蔡一智夫婦和林奕匡等撐場，其中林海峰和林奕匡更穿上「曹」字打氣T恤現身。<br />\n<br />\n林海峰完場後離開時表示曹星如雖然打不到十二個回合，但見對方已盡全力，受了傷仍堅持落去，他說：「打少咗一隻眼，好值得支持，今次打唔完場比賽，佢哋兩個應該都會想下次完成到比賽。」至於在現場觀戰的杜汶澤，賽後亦於facebook貼圖及留言謂：「Rex Win！」<br />\n<br />\n蔡一智夫婦<br />\n■眾藝人前晚去捧曹星如與前世界拳王河野公平比賽。<br />\n <br />\n鄭希怡<br />\n <br />\n林奕匡夫婦<br />\n <br />\n何超蕸<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n林嘉欣似自己打咗場<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【星級運動員】傅家俊李慧詩揚威國際<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲撐實至名歸<br />\n<br />\n林嘉欣似自己打咗場<br />\n<br />\n【星級運動員】傅家俊李慧詩揚威國際<br />\n<br />\n曹星如爭議勝仗　必有迴響張繼聰：挑戰心，大家學吓"},{"pid":"3826a44de1a2b3489372258dce408c894706b042","tid":430052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/09ec1p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F09ec1p10.jpg&h=8731d62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林奕匡夫婦"}]}